@startuml
title Viaverse Review / Trust / Badge / Gamification — Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "API Gateway / App BFF" as BFF
participant "trust-gamification-service" as Trust
participant "marketplace-service" as Marketplace
participant "moderation-service" as Moderation
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "Outbox / Kafka" as Kafka
participant "search/matching" as Search

Kafka -> Trust : JobCompleted
Trust -> DB : create ReviewPrompt x2

User -> Client : submit review
Client -> BFF : POST /reviews
BFF -> Trust : submitReview(command)
Trust -> Marketplace : validate job participant
Marketplace --> Trust : valid job/participant
Trust -> Moderation : scan text/tags
Moderation --> Trust : safe / queued / rejected
Trust -> DB : insert Review + ReviewTag
Trust -> Trust : calculate TrustScore + BadgeEligibility
Trust -> DB : persist score/badge/points
Trust -> Kafka : ReviewSubmitted
Trust -> Kafka : TrustScoreUpdated
Trust -> Kafka : BadgeAwarded
Kafka -> Search : update ranking projection
Kafka --> Client : notification / refresh profile

note bottom
Trust service validates job context but owns reviews,
trust score, badge state and gamification points.
end note
@enduml
